Practical No. 5

Aim: Compute Eigen values and Eigen vectors of given square array using
            python.

Q.1) Compute Eigenvalues and Eigenvectors of a given square array using python For 3x3 matrix.

Code:

import numpy as np

m = np.array([[3, 2, -1], [0, 5, 6], [0, 0, 9]])

print("Matrix:")
print(m)

w, v = np.linalg.eig(m)
print("Eigenvalues of the matrix:\n", w)
print("Eigenvectors of the matrix:\n", v)


Q.2) Compute Eigenvalues and Eigenvectors of a given square array 
     using python For 4x4 matrix.

Code:

import numpy as np

m = np.array([
    [3, 2, -1, 6],
    [0, 5, 6, 8],
    [0, 0, 9, 5],
    [6, 4, 8, 2]
])

print("Original Matrix:")
print(m)

w, v = np.linalg.eig(m)

print("Eigenvalues of the said matrix\n", w)
print("Eigenvectors of the said matrix\n", v)
